                    <h2>Lock Down</h2>
                    <p>You enter the looming façade of Cellblock 12, said to be the most haunted location inside the penitentiary. Rioting zombie have taken over, zombie guards have lost control, and the chaotic scene is filled with thick fog and mangled bars.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item card2">
                <img src="img/card2.jpg" alt="card 1">
                <div class="section-2-inner">
                    <h2>Machine Shop</h2>
                    <p>Hidden deep inside the cellblocks is a long-forgotten machine shop. Evil pervades this space – an evil with one mind but with many bodies. Will you survive, or will you become just another cog in the machine?</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item card3">
                <img src="img/card3.jpg" alt="card 1">
                <div class="section-2-inner">
                    <h2>Infirmary</h2>
                    <p>Infirmary takes the fear of hospitals to a whole new level. In this newly revamped and highly interactive attraction, you'll encounter maniacal surgeons, orderlies, dentists, and nurses who are sharpening their scalpels for some unusual, unnatural operations.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item card4">
                <img src="img/card4.jpg" alt="card 1">
                <div class="section-2-inner">
                    <h2>Blood Yard</h2>
                    <p>Deep within the ruins of the prison compound, you discover the camp of a gruesome colony. A path marked with bones leads you deeper into the lair of the butcher, the warriors, and their ancient empress - the forgotten who now reside among the fragments of the lost prison.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item card5">
                <img src="img/card5.jpg" alt="card 1">
                <div class="section-2-inner">
                    <h2>Quarantine 4D</h2>
                    <p>Inside, you learn of an infectious outbreak, whose symptoms include hallucinations, blurry vision, distorted depth perception, and other mind-altering effects. Flat walls appear to have depth, and some brave visitors will be challenged to face their WORST FEARS.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="item card6">
