                <div class="section-2-inner">
                    <h2>Break Out</h2>
                    <p>Just when you think you've found freedom, you find yourself in the middle of a prison break! Zombies surround you using every way imaginable to escape, including barrels, ropes, tunnels, ladders and crates.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
